com.polarion.alm.builder.model

Interface IBuildArtifact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAdaptable, IChangeListener, IHasValues, IPObject

    public interface IBuildArtifact
extends IPObject
    Build artifact.

    Smallest building/reporting entity.

    Identification (group and artifact ids) is modelled after Maven 2's artifact identification.

    Object id is unique within one getGroupEntity() and consists of getGroupId(), getArtifactId() and getRepositoryTag() (linked with colon ":").

    Version:
    $Revision: 519826 $ $Date: 2014-04-25 14:30:24 +0200 (Fri, 25 Apr 2014) $
    Author:
    Stepan Roh, Polarion Software

      • getBaseLocation

        ILocation getBaseLocation()
        Base location for this build artifact.

        Normally it is set to location of associated getGroupEntity(), but can be set to arbitrary location.

        Base location should contain all resources for this artifact (no resources should be located in parent folders or in other unrelated folders).

        May return null if and only if associated getGroupEntity() is not located in repository.

        Returns:
        base location or null in special case

      • getResources

        java.util.List getResources()
        Resources which comprise this artifact.

        Returned locations are relative to getBaseLocation().

        Is empty for project groups.

        Returns:
        List of ILocalDeploymentDefinitions (not null)
